Purpose

blocks.text: This Mutual Non I Disclosure Agreement outlines confidentiality obligations between the parties.
Each party agrees to protect all confidential information using reasonable measures.
This agreement remains in effect for three years from the effective date.
Neither party shall be liable for indirect or consequential damages.
